Uploading dashboard background and creating chart 9



Uploading dashboard background and creating chart


1.   Click the paint roller icon.

2.   Go to page background then click Add image.

3.   Select the image from your desktop and click open.

4.   Click line and clustered column chart.

5.   Drag Day of Week Name & Date to the shared axis.

6.   Remove day from Date.

7.   Drag Tornadoes Per Yr to Column values.

8.   Drag Cost per Tornado to line values.

 


How to create line and clustered column chart in power bi - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2d1JhcrhhGo
